stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: 创建任务
    Pending --> Running: 开始执行
    Running --> Completed: 成功完成
    Running --> Failed: 执行出错
    Running --> Cancelled: 用户取消
    Running --> TimedOut: 超时
    Failed --> Retrying: 可重试错误
    Retrying --> Running: 重试
    Retrying --> Failed: 超过重试上限
    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]: 清理资源
    Cancelled --> [*]: 清理资源
    TimedOut --> [*]: 清理资源
